  "bookSensorySignalsChapter1Title": "What are Sensory Signals?",
  "bookSensorySignalsChapter1Body": "Sensory signals are the way your child's body expresses its sensory needs.",
  "bookSensorySignalsChapter2Title": "How to Respond to Your Child's Signals?",
